content: Furthermore, if you import javax.swing.*; and import java.util.*;, and javax.swing.Queue is later added in a future version of Java, your code that uses Queue (java.util) will fail to compile.  This particular example is fairly unlikely, but if you are working with non-Oracle libraries, it may be more likely to happen.
